---
layout: base.njk
title: "Frequently Asked Questions — Heroes and Heritage Tours"
description: "Answers to common questions about group size, fitness level, what to bring, deposits and refunds, travel insurance, and booking logistics."
activeNav: faq
permalink: "/faq.html"
---

<header class="hero hero--compact">
  <div class="hero-media">
    <img src="/photos/flanders/flanders-05.jpg" alt="The Last Post Ceremony under the Menin Gate" width="1800" height="1200">
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">Frequently asked questions</span>
      <h1>Everything you need to know before you book.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Can't find your answer here? <a href="/contact.html" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: underline;">Get in touch</a> and we'll respond within one business day.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

{% for group in faq %}
<section class="section {% if loop.index0 is even %}{% else %}section--alt{% endif %}">
  <div class="container container--text">
    <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">{{ group.section }}</span>
      <h2>{{ group.heading }}</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list" data-reveal>
      {% for item in group.items %}
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          {{ item.q }}
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="11" y1="4" x2="11" y2="18"/><line x1="4" y1="11" x2="18" y2="11"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">{{ item.a | md | safe }}</div></div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endfor %}

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" style="background: var(--red);" data-reveal>
      <h2>Still have a question?</h2>
      <p class="lede">We reply to every message within one business day.</p>
      <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
